                            Email revenue per month · &lt;90 days · email
                            channel only
                        </p>

                        <blockquote
                            class="text-xl text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-8 italic"
                        >
                            "I'd definitely recommend e2. Jason and his whole
                            team has been incredible. The communication is
                            great, tons of resources pouring into our strategy.
                            Attributed revenue is up about 100% from where we
                            were. We went from sending 6–8 emails a month to 20+
                            and the results have been incredible."
                        </blockquote>

                        <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                            <div
                                class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-900 to-gray-900 border border-emerald-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-emerald-400 text-sm font-black flex-shrink-0"
