                            The 8-Year Partnership
                        </div>

                        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-8">
                            <div class="text-center">
                                <div
                                    class="text-4xl font-black text-gray-500 tracking-tight"
                                >
                                    $100k
                                </div>
                                <div
