                                >
                                    Month 1
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div
                                class="flex-1 flex items-center justify-center"
                            >
                                <div
                                    class="w-full h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-700 via-violet-500 to-gray-700"
                                >
                                </div>
                                <div
                                    class="absolute px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-violet-500/20 border border-violet-500/30 text-violet-400 text-sm font-black whitespace-nowrap"
                                >
                                    15×
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="text-center">
                                <div
                                    class="text-4xl font-black text-white tracking-tight"
                                >
                                    $1.5M
                                </div>
                                <div
                                    class="text-xs text-gray-400 font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide mt-1"
                                >
                                    Peak month
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <p
                            class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-6"
                        >
                            Monthly revenue · 8-year partnership · 7-figure exit
                            in 2021
                        </p>

                        <blockquote
                            class="text-xl text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-8 italic"
                        >
                            "I've been knowing Jason for about eight years. He's
                            worked on every project I've had, from $100k a month
                            to $1.5 million a month. I made a seven-figure exit
                            in 2021 with the canvas brand we worked on. Whoever
                            chooses to partner with Jason will be a smart
                            person. I hate doing these things because I feel
                            like I'm giving away my secret weapon."
                        </blockquote>

                        <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                            <div
                                class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-violet-900 to-gray-900 border border-violet-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-violet-400 text-sm font-black flex-shrink-0"
                            >
                                J
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <div class="font-bold text-white">
                                    Joshua Tatum
                                </div>
                                <div class="text-sm text-gray-400">
                                    Founder · Canvas Cultures
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
                        <BunnyVideo
                            libraryId="609841"
                            videoId="8d955164-4635-4902-899a-2ab1a15bb575"
                            title="Canvas Cultures: From $100k to $1.5M/Month"
                            subtitle="Joshua Tatum · Founder, Canvas Cultures"
                            author="Joshua Tatum"
                            authorRole="Founder, Canvas Cultures"
                        />
                        <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-3 text-center">
                            <div
                                class="rounded-xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10 p-4"
                            >
                                <div
                                    class="text-2xl font-black text-violet-400"
                                >
                                    15×
                                </div>
                                <div
                                    class="text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase font-semibold tracking-wide mt-1"
                                >
                                    Revenue multiple
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div
                                class="rounded-xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10 p-4"
                            >
                                <div class="text-2xl font-black text-white">
                                    7-fig
                                </div>
                                <div
                                    class="text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase font-semibold tracking-wide mt-1"
                                >
                                    Exit 2021
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div
                                class="rounded-xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10 p-4"
                            >
                                <div class="text-2xl font-black text-white">
                                    8 yrs
                                </div>
                                <div
                                    class="text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase font-semibold tracking-wide mt-1"
