                            pushing traffic. Two months in, it's above 30–40%.
                            We make way more money now. The pop-up split test
                            meant we collect way more leads too, without hurting
                            conversion rate at all."
                        </blockquote>

                        <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                            <div
                                class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-900 to-gray-900 border border-amber-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-amber-400 text-sm font-black flex-shrink-0"
